messages.message: It might be nice to surface the logged in user's email somewhere. I would expect my email to show up from either "My hub", the top right corner when i click on my initials, or from the usage/billing pages.
This makes sense, and we were thinking of adding this to the My Hub page. cc @alagu. We briefly looked into exposing the name + email but it got descoped.
How would you use it, @Junwon Jang ? Are you thinking of use cases where user has multiple accounts on AI hub and wants a quick confirmation of which account they have used to login?
